flowchart TD

Start([Start: User/Admin mengakses aplikasi])

Decision1{Pilih peran?}
Start --> Decision1

Decision1 --> User[User]
Decision1 --> Admin[Admin]

%% User Branch
User --> UserAction[Buka halaman utama]
UserAction --> DecisionUser{Pilih aksi?}
DecisionUser --> Survey[Survey]
DecisionUser --> Rekap[Rekap]

%% Survey Branch
Survey --> SurveyForm[Melihat form pendataan]
SurveyForm --> FillForm[Mengisi data koleksi]
FillForm --> SubmitForm[Submit form]
SubmitForm --> ValidateForm{Validasi form?}
ValidateForm --> Valid[Valid]
ValidateForm --> Invalid[Invalid]

Valid --> SaveDB[Simpan ke database]
SaveDB --> ThankYou[Tampilkan halaman terima kasih]
ThankYou --> End1([End])

Invalid --> ErrorMsg[Tampilkan error dan kembali ke form]
ErrorMsg --> End2([End])

%% Rekap Branch
Rekap --> RekapPage[Tampilkan halaman rekap dengan filter]
RekapPage --> LoadYear[Load data tahun dari database]
LoadYear --> SelectFilter[User pilih filter]
SelectFilter --> AjaxChart[AJAX request ke get_chart_stats]
AjaxChart --> QueryChart[Query agregat chart]
QueryChart --> ChartDecision{Data chart ada?}
ChartDecision --> YesChart[Ya]
ChartDecision --> NoChart[Tidak]

YesChart --> RenderCharts[Render 5 chart Chart.js]
RenderCharts --> StatCards[Tampilkan stat cards]

NoChart --> NoDataMsg[Tampilkan pesan tidak ada data]

StatCards --> AjaxTable[AJAX request ke get_rekap_data]
NoDataMsg --> AjaxTable

AjaxTable --> QueryTable[Query tabel data dengan pagination]
QueryTable --> RenderTable[Render tabel data]
RenderTable --> RefreshLoop{Ulangi load data?}
RefreshLoop --> YesRefresh[Ya]
YesRefresh --> SelectFilter
RefreshLoop --> NoRefresh[Tidak]
NoRefresh --> End3([End])

%% Admin Branch
Admin --> LoginPage[Buka halaman login admin]
LoginPage --> EnterCred[Masukkan kredensial]
EnterCred --> LoginDecision{Login valid?}
LoginDecision --> YesLogin[Ya]
LoginDecision --> NoLogin[Tidak]

YesLogin --> Dashboard[Tampilkan dashboard admin]
Dashboard --> MenuDecision{Pilih menu?}
MenuDecision --> ManagePendataan[Manajemen Pendataan]
MenuDecision --> DebugPendataan[Debug Pendataan]
MenuDecision --> Other[Lainnya]

ManagePendataan --> ListReports[Tampilkan daftar laporan pendataan]
ListReports --> ActionDecision{Aksi?}
ActionDecision --> Add[Tambah]
ActionDecision --> Edit[Edit]
ActionDecision --> Delete[Hapus]
ActionDecision --> Detail[Detail]
ActionDecision --> Back[Kembali]

Add --> AddForm[Tampilkan form tambah]
AddForm --> FillAdd[Admin isi form]
FillAdd --> SaveAdd[Simpan data baru]
SaveAdd --> RedirectList[Redirect ke daftar]
RedirectList --> End4([End])

Edit --> LoadEdit[Load data existing]
LoadEdit --> EditForm[Tampilkan form edit]
EditForm --> ChangeEdit[Admin ubah data]
ChangeEdit --> UpdateDB[Update database]
UpdateDB --> RedirectList2[Redirect ke daftar]
RedirectList2 --> End5([End])

Delete --> ConfirmDelete[Konfirmasi hapus]
ConfirmDelete --> DeleteDB[Delete data dari database]
DeleteDB --> RedirectList3[Redirect ke daftar]
RedirectList3 --> End6([End])

Detail --> ShowDetail[Tampilkan detail pendataan]
ShowDetail --> End7([End])

Back --> Dashboard

DebugPendataan --> VerifyAdmin[Verifikasi level admin]
VerifyAdmin --> DebugPage[Tampilkan halaman debug pendataan]
DebugPage --> End8([End])

Other --> OtherMenu[Akses menu lain]
OtherMenu --> End9([End])

NoLogin --> LoginFail[Tampilkan pesan login gagal]
LoginFail --> End10([End])